                     <interp inst="t18510203-481-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, stealing 1 wooden crate, and 72 glass bottles, value 12<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18510203-name-121" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18510203-name-121" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
